content: Missing some things. Here is the screenshot. We probably need Creator as well (which would be author or content creator). Or not if this is related to an Influencer, but do we want to make that required? what are your thoughts? I think that there is probably going to be content in here where I don't necessarily want them to influence more broadly, but think from a database standpoint, having additional information auto-captured would be beneficial. I'm assuming for new pieces of content, this could be done systematically and maybe we could add a flag to the Influencer tab to indicate whether their influencing is currently active (broad) or limited to only items in Knowledge Vault. Please also suggest reordering of columns logically, no explanation needed, just when you return the column review, order the way you best see fit.
